{"tid":966757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9假期【食是食非】10款港式甜品糖水卡路里＋運動時間！","createTime":"2019-01-03T04:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T04:54:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9e823a28ffdd6644db4da0ade1ec1dd112f326b5","tid":966757,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/787557/dining/甜品-糖水-卡路里-運動-跑步-芝麻糊/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F787557%2Fdining%2F%E7%94%9C%E5%93%81-%E7%B3%96%E6%B0%B4-%E5%8D%A1%E8%B7%AF%E9%87%8C-%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E8%B7%91%E6%AD%A5-%E8%8A%9D%E9%BA%BB%E7%B3%8A%2F&d=9M7Xd7PTM5cbQZimQZnUp4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=5857ff10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/787557/dining/甜品-糖水-卡路里-運動-跑步-芝麻糊/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/feature1_208079289459353d70bba76_9863361335a8505ff8e8d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Ffeature1_208079289459353d70bba76_9863361335a8505ff8e8d8.jpg&h=cef85fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放假與朋友聚餐後，少不免會食個甜品作為結尾，吃碗豆腐花、芝麻糊，幸福又滿足。但高興放縱過後，都要想想如何把吃下去的卡路里透過運動消耗，避免增肥。馬上看看營養師講解以下這些港式糖水的卡路里，再參考營養師提供的跑步時間，一於把卡路里通通跑走！<br />\n<br />\n10款港式甜品卡路里排行榜<br />\n<br />\n第10位 南北杏雪耳木瓜 約142卡路里/碗＝跑約18分鐘<br />\n<br />\n雪耳含植物性蛋白質，有助修補及滋潤皮膚；木瓜則含胡蘿蔔素，平衡皮膚油脂分泌，但要盡量少飲糖水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_01_104025131059351393b4bbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_01_104025131059351393b4bbf.jpg&h=89177cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第9位 豆腐花 約177卡路里/碗＝跑約23分鐘<br />\n<br />\n建議選擇無糖豆腐花或走糖水。如怕無糖口淡淡，可加配鮮果，那就好味又健康！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/201003171841311731943676_8767814105a851ac67c352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F201003171841311731943676_8767814105a851ac67c352.jpg&h=72dd8c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第8位 番薯糖水 約194卡路里/碗＝跑約25分鐘<br />\n<br />\n黃番薯高纖飽肚，含有胡蘿蔔素，平衡皮膚油脂分泌，減少乾燥甩皮，但同樣要少喝其糖水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_03_149160141759351416562be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_03_149160141759351416562be.jpg&h=7b6292ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第7位 榴槤班戟 約214卡路里/一客兩件＝跑約28分鐘<br />\n<br />\n榴槤的脂肪及卡路里都比較高，兩粒榴槤已等於一碗飯的卡路里，再加上忌廉，卡路里就更高！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_04_1887013865935145075fb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_04_1887013865935145075fb0.jpg&h=5c9757f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第6位 楊枝甘露 約254卡路里/碗＝跑約33分鐘<br />\n<br />\n芒果和西柚都含維他命C，本是個健康選擇。但坊間大多加入忌廉或椰汁，令其脂肪及卡路里偏高，卡路里跟一碗白飯差不多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_05-1_20115004195935148102a05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_05-1_20115004195935148102a05.jpg&h=85548e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第5位 芒果黑糯米 約290卡路里/碗＝跑約38分鐘<br />\n<br />\n黑糯米本身較健康，但芒果黑糯米當中最肥的成分是椰汁，怕肥的話最好走椰汁，再配芒果吃來增加甜度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_06-2_1318966168593515020a7bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_06-2_1318966168593515020a7bc.jpg&h=04cef29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4位 湯圓 約313卡路里/5粒＝跑約41分鐘<br />\n<br />\n湯圓內的麻蓉餡料有較多油，用糯米皮包着再加糖水，卡路里會比較高，建議選擇一些細粒、少點餡料的湯圓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_10_20273756505935153b7a322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_10_20273756505935153b7a322.jpg&h=780caf41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3位 芝麻糊 約320卡路里/碗＝跑約42分鐘<br />\n<br />\n黑芝麻含鐵質及鈣質，是頭髮生長必須的營養素，所包含的飽和脂肪亦令頭髮帶光澤，不過卡路里偏高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_09_3216693115935157457d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_09_3216693115935157457d9b.jpg&h=2cd8ac0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2位 腐竹雞蛋糖水 約342卡路里/碗＝跑約44分鐘<br />\n<br />\n腐竹其實是由豆漿浮面的那層豆油造成，脂肪含量不低。不過其油分屬有益，適合想增磅的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_07_14186541805935165b57a91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_07_14186541805935165b57a91.jpg&h=8b20a0e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第1位 涼粉西米露 約353卡路里/碗＝跑約46分鐘<br />\n<br />\n涼粉比較低卡，但溝椰汁西米露卻增加了不少卡路里，健康一點可配鮮果，並且要少糖水少椰汁，切記不要選罐頭雜果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_08_150343103259351617d0dab.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_08_150343103259351617d0dab.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=9M7Xd7PTM5cbQZimQZnUp4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=f12aad9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_08_150343103259351617d0dab.jpg[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"80607d44e084c6ea4686e41b84d2a3479d82e354","tid":966757,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wk_08_150343103259351617d0dab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fwk_08_150343103259351617d0dab.jpg&h=dddd319b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91212b0dd870c1b633d643e955bbdf8f9a72b472","tid":966757,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"閪茶呢"}]}